text: Amazingly delicious nasi padang, the lontong curry was so fragrant, pleasantly coconuty taste w the right amount of spice! Their belachan stands out too and packs a punch! I recommend their fried chicken wing, simple marinade but truly delicious. They offer a variety of classic side dishes and I would have love to tried the rest too!:)
The food here is a must! One week one time also can. One week never go, can become crazy.
